videos.description: Grant Wells passes it up the middle 22 yards to Xavier Gaines for Marshall's first touchdown of the season.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Marshall scores first on 22-yard TD) 2020/09/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Marshall scores first on 22-yard TD

videos.description: Brenden Knox forces his way with into the end zone for the 8-yard touchdown, but not without the help of some linemen helping him push past the defense.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Knox gets a push into the end zone for a Marshall TD) 2020/09/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Knox gets a push into the end zone for a Marshall TD

videos.description: Before the game, Eastern Kentucky players and staff members raise awareness of social injustice with shirts that read "Say their names" and "Enough is enough."

videos.headline: EKU players and staff wear 'Say their names' shirts

videos.description: Grant Wells launches a 21-yard pass to a double-covered Talik Keaton for another Thundering Herd touchdown.

videos.headline: Wells connects with Keaton for a 21-yard Marshall TD

videos.description: Grant Wells keeps extending Marshall's lead over Eastern Kentucky, connecting with Jaron Woodyard on a 42-yard touchdown pass.
